Quote:  Male that cannot get a female pregnant. An entire male is made into a teaser by: Vasectomising ...Penis deviation ... Treating a female with male hormone to sexually activate her and make her act like a male ...Tie an apron on an entire male which prevents his penis entering the female when he mounts ... .
